Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.55,0:11:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,鶴乃 不是的 不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.86,0:11:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,已經無法努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.90,0:11:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不想再努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.09,0:11:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,對我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.91,0:11:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,已經一無所有了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.46,0:11:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.15,0:11:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.11,0:11:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.12,0:11:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,把鶴乃逼到了絕境
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.91,0:11:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,八千代
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.94,0:11:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我 剛剛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.62,0:11:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,連攜將精神連接上了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.41,0:12:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,鶴乃是最強的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.39,0:12:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,比誰都強
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.34,0:12:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不能說謊 鶴乃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.94,0:12:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,鶴乃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.77,0:12:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,強大所以沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.27,0:12:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.05,0:12:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,哪裡沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.32,0:12:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,菲莉希亞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.54,0:12:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,已經夠了吧 你根本不強吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.56,0:12:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不用再努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.18,0:12:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,再忍下去 一輩子都沒法改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.93,0:12:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,菲莉希亞 你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.05,0:12:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,八千代你也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.57,0:12:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我才是原因
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.71,0:12:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是我寄予了厚望 希望鶴乃變強
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.01,0:12:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我束縛了鶴乃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.19,0:12:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,八千代 再和鶴乃連攜一次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.93,0:12:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果再失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.68,0:13:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,沒問題的 八千代你也一定明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.81,0:13:10.39,ObjectText,,0,0,400,,{\an2\fn大赦宋体 DemiBold\fsp10\c&HE0D3D7&\fad(900,1200)\blur0.8}正確的魔法少女
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.47,0:13:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我對大家太嚴格了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.13,0:13:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,八千代你對自己也一樣嚴格
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.57,0:13:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,其實沒有人真的那麼強大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.76,0:13:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,八千代 希望今後鶴乃變成什麼樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.11,0:13:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,希望鶴乃 不用再裝作強大了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.62,0:13:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我們就這樣保持弱小
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.72,0:13:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,相互扶持吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.59,0:13:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,彩羽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.55,0:13:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,已經沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.37,0:13:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,看上去總算是趕上了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.92,0:13:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,桃子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.34,0:13:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.01,0:14:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,遲到很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.23,0:14:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,美冬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.53,0:14:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,背後就交給我們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.90,0:14:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,鶴乃就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.12,0:14:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,鶴乃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.33,0:14:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,給我老實點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.62,0:14:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我也齊心協力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.29,0:14:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.55,0:14:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你並不希望成為最強
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.99,0:14:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你其實沒有必須變強的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.01,0:14:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,痛苦的事 明天和大家一起煩惱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.85,0:14:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 鶴乃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.01,0:15:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,沙耶加 我們也
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.30,0:15:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,麻美學姐雖然是指引了我們的強大前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.25,0:15:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,或許她一直在勉強自己
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.80,0:15:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,全都是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.99,0:15:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,所以必須拯救
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.79,0:15:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,要被解開了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.75,0:15:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.56,0:15:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,真正的麻美學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.51,0:15:52.26,ObjectText,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fn大赦黑体 DemiBold\c&H4FABC0&\blur0.5\fs56\pos(101,670)}無論發生什麼，我都會拯救大家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.43,0:15:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,回來吧 麻美學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.31,0:15:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Tiro Duet
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.85,0:16:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.77,0:16:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,小圓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.01,0:16:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,連攜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.21,0:16:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,魔女在逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.23,0:16:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,做到了 成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.36,0:17:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,真是讓人費心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.45,0:17:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.30,0:17:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.34,0:17:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,八千代
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.74,0:17:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,鶴乃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.71,0:17:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,鶴乃 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.11,0:17:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 對不起大家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.80,0:17:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是我錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.09,0:17:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起鶴乃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.09,0:17:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,菲莉希亞 也讓我向你致歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.52,0:17:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,八千代
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.67,0:17:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的 八千代
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.00,0:17:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,即使錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.80,0:17:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,今後改正就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.01,0:17:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.87,0:17:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,桃子 美冬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.61,0:17:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,鶴乃能回來都是多虧了你們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.99,0:17:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,作為我的贖罪還遠遠不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.81,0:17:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好不容易大家又像這樣聚在了一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.43,0:17:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不必再說了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.03,0:18:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 真的
