Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.65,0:18:12.53,ObjectText,,0,0,0,,{\an1\b1\fs42\c&H9B1C68&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord3\pos(1418,721)}見瀧原市 避難勸告發布\n{\c&H5C54D5&\fs40}請前往各自治體避難所避難
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.28,0:18:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是說魔女之夜要去見瀧原嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.49,0:18:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,得回見瀧原
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.09,0:18:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 如果現在鹿目回了見瀧原
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.62,0:18:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.25,0:18:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,彩羽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.27,0:18:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,希望你的願望 能夠實現
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.40,0:18:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.28,0:19:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,現在的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.07,0:19:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.72,0:19:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,有在恢復嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.47,0:19:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我又精神飽滿了 彩羽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.89,0:19:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,環
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.29,0:19:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你覺得自己能加入那邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.45,0:19:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你和那些人不一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.00,0:19:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你有對弱小的我伸出援手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.57,0:19:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.50,0:19:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.37,0:19:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你 無法加入進去的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.55,0:19:55.05,ObjectText,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\pos(980,640)\b1\fsp15}為什麼想加入她們的故事？
