Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.55,0:19:57.80,ObjectText,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\pos(980,640)\b1\fsp15}你有這樣的權利嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.59,0:20:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,她們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.05,0:20:01.30,ObjectText,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\b1\fsp15\pos(980,320)}你最好被遺忘。
