Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.82,0:20:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,和你不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.31,0:20:06.06,ObjectText,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\b1\fsp15\pos(980,320)}幼稚的想法救不了你。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.31,0:20:06.06,ObjectText,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\b1\fsp15\pos(980,925)}她不理解你 亦不理解她的妹妹們。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.31,0:20:06.06,Runes,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\pos(960,570)\fs55}SHE DOESN'T\nUNDERSTAND YOU\nOR HER YOUNGER SISTERS.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.06,0:20:10.06,EPTitle,,0,0,125,,{\c&H8171DE&}你根本就不強吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.66,0:20:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,就算不強 我也會贏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.23,0:20:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那兒
